  - <ID>k__BackingField: 87bc91e4-0d69-4f13-aba9-30a1369355a5
    <Name>k__BackingField: Ending02
    <Text>k__BackingField: Today has been a lot, but it feels like I made some progress.
      Talking about the different events that have been bothering me lately feels
      good.
    <Choices>k__BackingField:
    - <Text>k__BackingField: Next Dialogue
      <NodeID>k__BackingField: d66c6ac7-5d89-4897-85dd-cb0eb7511039
    <GroupID>k__BackingField: 
    <DialogueType>k__BackingField: 0
    <Position>k__BackingField: {x: 363, y: -267}
  - <ID>k__BackingField: d1b37212-3a44-4dd9-bb27-0bda9e53ee99
    <Name>k__BackingField: Ending04
    <Text>k__BackingField: "The psychologist told me that I\u2019ve been bothered
      by these thoughts for a long time probably without thinking about them."
    <Choices>k__BackingField:
    - <Text>k__BackingField: Next Dialogue
      <NodeID>k__BackingField: 950efb5b-eaa6-4bd7-a584-ee45028b79f1
    <GroupID>k__BackingField: 
    <DialogueType>k__BackingField: 0
    <Position>k__BackingField: {x: 54, y: 67}
  - <ID>k__BackingField: d66c6ac7-5d89-4897-85dd-cb0eb7511039
    <Name>k__BackingField: Ending03
    <Text>k__BackingField: The psychologist seems happy with me opening up and says
      that they have a better understanding about what is bothering me.
    <Choices>k__BackingField:
    - <Text>k__BackingField: Next Dialogue
      <NodeID>k__BackingField: d1b37212-3a44-4dd9-bb27-0bda9e53ee99
    <GroupID>k__BackingField: 
    <DialogueType>k__BackingField: 0
    <Position>k__BackingField: {x: 1116, y: -253}
  - <ID>k__BackingField: 950efb5b-eaa6-4bd7-a584-ee45028b79f1
    <Name>k__BackingField: Ending05
    <Text>k__BackingField: Me falling into the water caused me to develop a fear
      that my parents ignored and thought I would forget. Playing with toys and building
      snowmen were just a coping mechanism for me to avoid thinking about the bad
      thoughts.
    <Choices>k__BackingField:
    - <Text>k__BackingField: Next Dialogue
      <NodeID>k__BackingField: 5ff19ea0-a0b9-4c23-8367-93f13b84cf6a
    <GroupID>k__BackingField: 
    <DialogueType>k__BackingField: 0
    <Position>k__BackingField: {x: 755, y: 67}
  - <ID>k__BackingField: 5ff19ea0-a0b9-4c23-8367-93f13b84cf6a
    <Name>k__BackingField: Ending06
    <Text>k__BackingField: The problem resurfaced at work whenever I was stressing
      too much causing me to have a mental breakdown. Now I am aware of my condition
      and can avoid scenes that cause stress.
    <Choices>k__BackingField:
    - <Text>k__BackingField: Next Dialogue
      <NodeID>k__BackingField: b5ffe9ea-0079-417b-94fe-9b447aaec293
    <GroupID>k__BackingField: 
    <DialogueType>k__BackingField: 0
    <Position>k__BackingField: {x: 46, y: 350}
  - <ID>k__BackingField: b5ffe9ea-0079-417b-94fe-9b447aaec293
    <Name>k__BackingField: Ending07
    <Text>k__BackingField: "Thank god i talked honestly to my psychologist, it has
      really improved things for me, but there\u2019s still a lot of work ahead.\r\n"
    <Choices>k__BackingField:
    - <Text>k__BackingField: Next Dialogue
      <NodeID>k__BackingField: 
    <GroupID>k__BackingField: 
    <DialogueType>k__BackingField: 0
